{
  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT-4 and Gemini were chosen for this study primarily because of their multimodal structures, which support the seamless management of multidisciplinary clinical scenarios.",
    "They are, as well, among the most widely adopted and easily obtainable AI chatbots available today [4,10].",
    "Furthermore, the PDFenabled ChatGPT is a feature that can be used specifically with the ChatGPT-4 version.",
    "With this add-on, ChatGPT can read, analyze, and extract information about the content based on the questions posed regarding uploaded PDF files [27].",
    "The reason for preferring PDF-enabled ChatGPT-4 in this study was not only to examine the accuracy of its responses regarding RET procedures but also to demonstrate whether physicians in the healthcare field can obtain necessary information more quickly by querying AI chatbots about comprehensive PDFs."
  ]
}